<p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">母亲节，是一个感谢母亲的节日，时间为每年5月的第二个星期日。为了庆祝这个意义非凡的时刻，经济管理学院学生会特此发起“笔墨寄深情，家书抵万金”母亲</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">节家书征集活动。下面让我们一起来看看同学们是如何向母亲倾诉心底的爱与感恩吧！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">花点时间，听听她的烦恼心事；花</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">点时间，听听她的回忆故事；花点时间，听听她的唠叨琐事。世界再大，也走不出她对你的爱，这一生的浪漫和宠溺记得留给妈妈一份。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">以下是经管学子们和妈妈的温馨留影瞬间：</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220501朱滢</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587550169058319.png" title="1715587550169058319.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">C220515李悦</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587584228022719.png" title="1715587584228022719.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230508凃可欣</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587613345030738.png" title="1715587613345030738.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">C220520魏智</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587641993040250.png" title="1715587641993040250.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220507钟婷</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587676309083535.png" title="1715587676309083535.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220502余平平</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587703058026574.png" title="1715587703058026574.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220501万可心</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587726403088558.png" title="1715587726403088558.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220501郭毓</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587752468075817.png" title="1715587752468075817.png" alt="image.png"/><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">经管学子对妈妈的温情表白时刻:</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220510辛婷婷</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587792243005843.png" title="1715587792243005843.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230501刘欣洁</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587816462028878.png" title="1715587816462028878.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230501王乐熙</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587843312060865.png" title="1715587843312060865.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230503徐文菲</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587869297088154.png" title="1715587869297088154.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230507赵璇</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587891902083424.png" title="1715587891902083424.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230508李小敏</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587918632027761.png" title="1715587918632027761.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230508刘诗雨</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587943396086093.png" title="1715587943396086093.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230509许心怡</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715587978623054176.png" title="1715587978623054176.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">C230513郭梦寒</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715588005168033643.png" title="1715588005168033643.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">C230513王婷</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715588029442097293.png" title="1715588029442097293.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">C230513邹春兰</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715588124220056569.png" title="1715588124220056569.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B220510乐景莎</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715588148611015138.png" title="1715588148611015138.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">B230507彭欣逸</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em; text-align: center;"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240513/1715588173820091603.png" title="1715588173820091603.png" alt="image.png"/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><br/></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">五月浅夏，时光斑斓。这是一个深情的季节，所有与爱有关的事物都在发芽。母亲节，在这温暖的月份里如约而至。每年的母亲节，只有一天，但是母亲对我们的爱，却是岁岁年年。在节日到来之际，让我们以爱之名，大胆地给她告白吧！</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">母爱是柴米油盐中的琐碎细腻，是无数次辗转低回的牵挂。母亲的爱比宇宙永恒，比天地广阔，比太阳温暖，温柔了我们的童年时光，给了我们成年时拥抱世界的力量。纸短情长，母亲节只是五月的一天，而妈妈爱了我们一年又一年。</span></p><p style="text-indent: 2em;"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 18px;">当你羽翼日渐丰满，离开家乡，请记得家乡的妈妈，常回家看看!今天我们将所有的思念、感恩、爱揉成一句话：妈妈，我爱您，祝您节日快乐！</span></p>